First part Question No 36 by ( H-0025 / 00 ) : Subject : High infant mortality in Kosovo According to the latest UN data received from the World Health Organisation , Kosovo has the highest rate of infant mortality in Europe ; almost 50 % of babies born prematurely die , while the war has produced a steep rise in miscarriages and children who manage to go to term are smaller than the norm .
