Question No 39 by ( H-0036 / 00 ) : Subject : Drafting of Charter of Fundamental Rights The general public welcomes the fact that a Charter of Fundamental Rights is to be drawn up .
It is also to be hoped that it will meet the challenges of Europe in the 21st century .
